{"article_id":"sbY6IBKplNrJZRGf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Small-town police chief killed","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"as officers in 3 cities wounded during violence at George Floyd protests","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"An officer in Las Vegas reportedly was on life support","depth":13},{"id":3,"text":"after being shot .","depth":13},{"id":4,"text":"A retired St. Louis police captain","depth":15},{"id":5,"text":"who became a small-town police chief","depth":15},{"id":6,"text":"was found fatally shot early Tuesday outside a pawn shop","depth":15},{"id":7,"text":"that was looted","depth":15},{"id":8,"text":"after protests over the death of George Floyd turned violent .","depth":13},{"id":9,"text":"David Dorn , 77 , was discovered on the sidewalk in front of Lee 's Pawn & Jewelry in St. Louis around 2:30 a.m. ,","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"said Police Commissioner John Hayden .","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"Dorn ,","depth":15},{"id":13,"text":"who retired from the St. Louis Police Department in 2007","depth":16},{"id":14,"text":"and had been serving as police chief of Moline Acres , Missouri , since 2008 ,","depth":16},{"id":15,"text":"was killed","depth":14},{"id":16,"text":"when he apparently tried to stop the looting of the shop .","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"`` David Dorn was exercising law enforcement training","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"that he learned here , ''","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"Hayden said .","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"No further details were immediately released .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"His widow , Ann Marie Dorn , told the St. Louis Post-Dispatch","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that her husband was a friend of the pawn shop 's owner","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and frequently checked on the business","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"when alarms went off .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"David Dorn , a 77-year-old retired St. Louis police officer","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"who served 38 years on the force","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"was shot and killed by looters at a pawn shop early , June 2 , 2020 ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"police said .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Scott Bandle/Suburban Journals/St . Louis Post-Dispatch via AP","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"The death came on a brutal night for police across the country .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"A Las Vegas police officer on life support was last listed in critical condition","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"after being shot Monday night","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"attempting to disperse a large crowd of protesters outside a casino ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"authorities said .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"An officer was attacked in New York City ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and four cops were shot in St. Louis","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"as demonstrations across the nation in the aftermath of George Floyd 's death have turned increasingly violent for both protesters and police .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"At least five deaths have occurred during the widespread unrest ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"according to The New York Times .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Las Vegas Metropolitan Police Department Officer Shay Mikalonis , 29 , was critically wounded","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"engaging with violent protesters outside the Circus Circus Hotel & Casino on the famed Las Vegas Strip .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Separately , police fatally shot a heavily armed man","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"who appeared to be wearing body armor","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"outside a federal courthouse nearby .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"`` This is a sad night for LVMPD family and a tragic night for our community , ''","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"LVMPD Sheriff Joe Lombardo said at a news conference .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"`` With these protests ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"which are leading to riots ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"one tragedy is only leading to another . ''","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Lombardo said","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"his officers were being pelted with rocks and bottles .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"`` Our officers were attempting to get some of the protesters in custody","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"when a shot rang out","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"and our officer went down , ''","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"he added .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Mikalonis was taken to Las Vegas University Medical Center ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"where he was in `` extremely critical condition . ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Police officials said","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"he underwent surgery","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"to remove a bullet from his neck .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"A suspect was arrested by a SWAT team ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"but that person 's name was n't immediately released ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Lombardo added .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"A member of the St. Louis Fire Department removes a hose outside a vandalized and burned convenience store , June 2 , 2020 , in St. Louis , the morning after protests against the death of George Floyd .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"People were seen removing items from the store","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"before the building went up in flames","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"following a large peaceful protest .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Jeff Roberson/AP","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"While LVMPD officers were investigating the shooting ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"officers","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"guarding the Foley Federal Building","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"were confronted by an armed man around 11:22 p.m. ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Lombardo said .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"That suspect ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"who appeared to be wearing body armor ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"had multiple firearms .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"`` During the interaction , the subject reached for his firearm","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"and our officers engaged him , ''","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Lombardo said .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"The suspect ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"who has n't yet been identified ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"died at the hospital .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"It 's unclear whether that individual had been among the protesters ,","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Lombardo added .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"The four officers","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"wounded in St. Louis on Monday night","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"were shot near police headquarters ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"where clashes with rioters lasted well into the night .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"`` They were standing near a line","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"and all of a sudden they felt pain , ''","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Police Commissioner Hayden said during a news conference Tuesday morning .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"`` They were just standing there .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"So some coward fired shots at officers ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"and now we have four in the hospital ...","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"and thank God","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"they 're alive .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Can we make some sense out of this ? ...","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"This is horrible . ''","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"The officers ,","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"ranging in age from 28 to 52 ,","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"suffered non-life-threatening injuries .","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"Before the shootings , demonstrators hurled rocks and fireworks at police ,","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"and some officers had gasoline dumped on them ,","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"Hayden added .","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"Meanwhile in New York City , video emerged","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"that appeared to show an officer","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"being attacked with a heavy object by a group of men in the Bronx .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"The New York Police Department said","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"it made nearly 700 arrests Monday night","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"as looting and vandalism targets included stores at Rockefeller Center and some in the Upper East Side .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"A curfew of 11 p.m. had been put in effect .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"`` We saw stuff last night","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that we will not accept .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"And we can fight back ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"and we will fight back , ''","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"Mayor Bill de Blasio said at a news conference on Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"`` I have confidence in the people of New York City ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"I have confidence in the leaders in communities ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"I have confidence in the NYPD . `","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"` There 's a lot of people","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"trying to express fear ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"a lot of people","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"trying to tear down ,","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"a lot of people say","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"they do n't believe in the people of this city ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"they do n't believe in people in our communities ,","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"they do n't believe in our police officers .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"To hell with all of them .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"I do n't care","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"if they 're left or right or center --","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"I am sick of people","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"attacking New York City . ''","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Floyd died May 25 in Minneapolis .","depth":2},{"id":134,"text":"His final moments were captured in a searing video of a white officer with his knee on Floyd 's black neck","depth":4},{"id":135,"text":"as he pleaded for his life .","depth":4},{"id":136,"text":"`` I ca n't breathe , ''","depth":4},{"id":137,"text":"Floyd said .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"p